data.description: Do not miss this nicely maintained and updated 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom, 1939 bungalow with 1-car detached garage, located in Canon City's beautiful tree-lined Grand Avenue in Lincoln Park neighborhood, just outside the city limits! You will love how cozy and efficient this home is, and how spacious the 1044 sq ft floor plan feels! From the large living room and bright, sunny kitchen/dining combo, laminate and tile flooring, chair rail and crown molding, full bath with stylish tile and built-in storage cabinet, this home feels much newer and bigger than advertised. All appliances included. Brand new roof installed September 2023! Tremendous curb appeal with lush green lawn, built in benches on front porch, and large driveway equipped for RV parking and power supply hookup. Private and shady backyard with covered brick-paver patio, mature shade trees, raised garden beds, fire pit, and built-in serving bar—all ready for entertaining and relaxation. RV hookups in the side yard. Large storage shed, with additional workshop space available in the detached garage with heater and 3/4 bath. What a wonderful place to call home, come see today and make it yours!
